---===### Deathrun_Wood ###===---


File size: 10 Mb (3 Mb zipped)

Spawn points: 32 (31 CT and only 1 T)

Trap information:

Trap 1 - Oval spinning thing
Trap 2 - Propeller (Picture 4)
Trap 3 - Large crusher
Trap 4 - Lid over landing Water
Trap 5 - Laser
Trap 6 - Disappearing plasma bridge (Picture 3)
Trap 7 - Wall crucher
Trap 8 - Fire room (Picture 6)
Trap 9 - Teleport floor to death chamber
Trap 10 - Exploding barrels
Trap 11 - Hard to explain -_-
Trap 12 - Random breakable platforms over dangerous water
Trap 13 - Spinning laser pillar (Picture 5)

Hidden smoke grenades: 5 (3 in the start and 2 on the deathrun)

You can only click the buttons once to prevent dubbel puching.


If you want me to make some small modifications to the map, please leave a comment and tell me so.
